.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, lemonade, tea
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, thriller, musical, romance
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, cricket, golf, handball
1. the person who's sport is handball is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking fanta##2
2. the person who's sport is handball is the person drinking tea##1
3. the person watching musical movies is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
6. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
7. the person who's sport is handball is between the person who's sport is golf and the person watching sports movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | tea      | fanta       | lemonade   |
| Movie-Genre      | sports   | thriller  | romance | musical     |
| Sport      | cricket     | handball | golf        | basketball |

