.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, camping, cooking, sudoku
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, skateboarding, golf, biathlon
4 different pets are kept: hamster, horse, lizard, rabbit
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the owner of the rabbit and the person who's hobby is camping##2
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
4. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
5. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | sudoku  | camping | cooking | board-games |
| Sport   | handball  | biathlon | skateboarding   | golf         |
| Pet           | hamster | lizard  | horse   | rabbit      |

