.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-10::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, orange, pepper, pomegranate
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, nurse, architect, chef
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, fantasy, time-travel
1. the chef is on the far left##1
2. the person eating pepper is on the far left##1
3. the person eating orange is between the person eating lettuce and the nurse##2
4. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
5. the architect is on the far right##1
6. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
7. the person watching time-travel movies is the chef##1
8. the person watching adventure movies is the person eating pomegranate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | pepper      | pomegranate | orange | lettuce |
| Job         | chef   | nurse  | project-manager | architect |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | adventure   | comedy | fantasy |

