The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, gardening, sudoku, traveling
4 different games are played: whist, poker, mah-jongg, domino
1. the person playing poker is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person drinking juice##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking juice and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person playing poker##1
6. the person playing whist is on the far right##1
7. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | mirinda | juice     | almond-milk | 7up       |
| Hobby      | sudoku  | traveling | card-games  | gardening |
| Game        | domino  | poker      | mah-jongg        | whist      |

