3. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
6. the person drinking water is the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
