The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, fantasy, romance, time-travel
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, cain, blend, dannemann
1. the person watching disaster movies is the dannemann-smoker##1
2. the blend-smoker is the mechanic##1
3. the blend-smoker is on the left of the dancer##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
5. the cain-smoker is between the person watching romance movies and the mechanic##2
6. the dannemann-smoker is on the far right##1
7. the cain-smoker is the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Job           | entrepreneur | scientist | mechanic    | dancer   |
| Movie-Genre   | romance      | fantasy   | time-travel | disaster |
| Cigar     | prince     | cain       | blend        | dannemann    |

