The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, funk, rock, soul
4 different pets are kept: turtle, snake, hamster, rat
1. the fan of country is the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person drinking cola is between the person drinking mirinda and the owner of the snake##2
3. the person drinking mirinda is the fan of funk##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is between the fan of rock and the owner of the rat##2
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the owner of the turtle is between the owner of the hamster and the fan of soul##2
7. the fan of country is the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | mirinda | cola   | soy-milk |
| Music-Genre   | country  | funk    | rock   | soul     |
| Pet   | rat  | hamster | turtle | snake   |

