.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-19::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, freelancer, journalist, librarian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, snowboarding, surfing, weightlifting
There are 4 different favourite colors: emerald, amber, purple, green
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the journalist##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person who likes emerald##1
3. the dancer is on the far left##1
4. the person who likes purple is the librarian##1
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person who likes purple##1
6. the person who likes green is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person who likes purple##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | dancer        | librarian  | journalist | freelancer   |
| Sport       | weightlifting | ice-hockey | surfing    | snowboarding |
| Color   | emerald        | purple     | green       | amber      |

